 * Accepts the same options as `useStream` from `@langchain/react`, plus
 * `cloud` and `adapters`.
 *
 * @example
 * ```tsx
 * import { useStreamRuntime } from "@assistant-ui/react-langchain";
 * import { AssistantRuntimeProvider, Thread } from "@assistant-ui/react";
 *
 * function App() {
